Class DelegatingCommandStack

java.lang.Object
  org.eclipse.gef.commands.CommandStack
      ccm.editors.tools.DelegatingCommandStack
All Implemented Interfaces:
org.eclipse.gef.commands.CommandStackListener
public class DelegatingCommandStack
extends org.eclipse.gef.commands.CommandStack
implements org.eclipse.gef.commands.CommandStackListener

This is a delegating command stack, which delegates everything a defined the CommandStack except event listners.

Event listeners registered to a DelegatingCommandStack will be informed whenever the underlying CommandStack changes. They will not be registered to the underlying CommandStack but they will be informed about change events of them.

Author:
Gunnar Wagenknecht
